faith.name: Faith
faith.definition: to be firmly persuaded of God’s power and promises to accomplish His will and purpose and to display such a confidence in Him and His Word that circumstances and obstacles do not shake that conviction

exhortation.name: Exhortation
exhortation.definition: to come along side of someone with words of encouragement, comfort, consolation, and counsel to help them be all God wants them to be

knowledge.name: Knowledge
knowledge.definition: to seek to learn as much about the Bible as possible through the gathering of much information and the analyzing of that data
